    answer: "Post a single reply in any DM thread and the conversation transfers to you permanently. Most demolition firms let the AI capture the opening brief — building type, frame construction, floor area, asbestos survey status, programme timeline, and tender deadline — then engage personally to discuss plant deployment, access logistics, crushing arrangements, and commercial terms."
